The Nigerian first Lady, Aisha Buhari has finally returned to the country after spending six months in Dubai, United Arab Emirates.  Mrs. Buhari arrived in Nigeria on Wednesday night, March 17, and is currently in the statehouse, Abuja. The first lady quietly travelled to Dubai after Hanan, one of her daughters, got married in September 2020.  Source The wife of the President and First Lady of Nigeria, Mrs Aisha Buhari, has allegedly relocated to Dubai, United Arab Emirates, according to a report by SaharaReporters. Aisha's husband, President Buhari assumed office on 29 May 2015 after he defeated the then-incumbent President Goodluck Jonathan. Aisha is a cosmetologist, beauty… In "Politics" According to SaharaReporters, it has been revealed that Nigeria’s First Lady, Mrs Aisha Buhari, is currently in Dubai, United Arab Emirates.   Aisha traveled to Dubai with her entourage ahead of the expected delivery of a baby by her daughter, Zahra.   This revelation is against widespread belief that Mrs… In "News" The First Lady, Mrs Aisha Buhari, has been flown out of the country to Dubai, in the United Arab Emirate. Although the office of the First Lady could not confirm the reason for her trip, there are strong indications that Mrs Buhari may be receiving medical attention in the Arab… In "News"